    | displayName |
    | Staff       |
    And the following users:
      | givenName | sn     | uid   | password | school_admin | role_name | puavoEduPersonAffiliation |
      | Pavel     | Taylor | pavel | secret   | true         | Staff     | Staff                     |
    And I am logged in as "cucumber" with password "cucumber"
  
